{"tid":514173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"子命喪海洋公園鬼屋　母幾乎哭盲","createTime":"2017-12-30T09:42:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T05:54:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"b661899a3477633a294b543e88da07982331328e","tid":514173,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T09:42:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171230/20259960\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171230%2F20259960&d=K2ZWUtMstStDIes0vZ4PKrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=92e394c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171230%2F20259960&h=b5d41f2f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171230/20259960</a><br />\n<br />\n子命喪海洋公園鬼屋　母幾乎哭盲<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年9月16日，21歲青年張朝傑與女友到海洋公園試玩萬聖節鬼屋「活埋凶間」時，誤闖後勤設施遭「棺材」擊中頭部死亡。事隔3個月，傑仔父母仍未走出傷痛，與傑仔感情深厚的媽媽更因傷心過度以淚洗面，致眼疾惡化幾乎哭盲，現時右眼只剩兩成視力，擔心未來活在朦朧中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171230/large/a0803a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171230%2Flarge%2Fa0803a.gif&h=2dcbac06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n肥媽盼警方早日交代意外成因，讓傑仔（小圖）安息。麥超億攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171230/large/30la7p33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171230%2Flarge%2F30la7p33.jpg&h=86c1b9b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n傑仔3個月前於鬼屋「活埋凶間」出事。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171230/large/a0803b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171230%2Flarge%2Fa0803b.gif&h=a344abe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傷痛未平　憂無錢求醫<br />\n<br />\n「冇辦法啦&hellip;&hellip;」傑仔父母在接受《蘋果》訪問時最常說這句話，兩人都說意外突然，傑仔是家中長子，他跟母親感情特別好，愛稱媽媽做「肥媽」，悲傷未平服，肥媽最懷念昔日一家四口同枱食飯的情景，為免觸景傷情，他們把傑仔舊照統統收起，睡床亦拆走，「以前6、7 點，一家人一齊食飯，𠵱家冇喇」。<br />\n<br />\n念舊日，點滴在心頭，肥媽難忘傑仔乖巧和自律，意外前傑仔透露兩年後畢業會從事電子工程養家，現在他們只能去道堂拜祭。她無奈說︰「當佢去旅行囉！」說罷悲從中來飲泣落淚，她稱事發後「瞓又瞓唔到，成個黐線婆咁」。更嚴重是眼疾惡化，幾乎哭盲，她指十多年前因糖尿病影響視力，「傑仔過身後喊太多，隻眼就差」。<br />\n<br />\n肥媽今年9月因眼疾求診，10月的覆診日遇上傑仔出殯，院方更改覆診日期，其後檢查發現其右眼只剩兩成視力。<br />\n<br />\n喪子傷痛未平服，又受眼疾困擾，肥媽表示現時多數留在家中，因日間陽光猛烈會頭暈，亦怕視力不好會跌傷。現時一家人靠3,000多元綜援金及丈夫做兼職維持生計，擔心無力支付眼疾醫療費用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n\t茶記大爆炸　險死店員從頭起步<br />\n港聞 8小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t創傷後壓力症或需情景治療<br />\n港聞 8小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t死裏逃生　有幸有不幸<br />\n港聞 8小時前"},{"pid":"2264f90985909fa178257359b24744797672f3c5","tid":514173,"uid":73856,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T09:46:40.000Z","msg":"慘"},{"pid":"3770c43d7d5ba5485be6a7ae2db0fed16f1d35e6","tid":514173,"uid":132038,"like":14,"dislike":357,"score":-343,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T09:49:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6fbbc5db5c974a77bc5f380be6b9f67afd989107","tid":514173,"uid":94739,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T09:49:51.000Z","msg":"心都酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e9182570303c959fe59bdcde47cbdc46ae78b29","tid":514173,"uid":550,"like":157,"dislike":0,"score":157,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T09:53:06.000Z","msg":"真係冇辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n邊個諗到去海馬公園都會死人"},{"pid":"e79fce0de3e9ff733f22f73fadc994a90ab37986","tid":514173,"uid":11097,"like":249,"dislike":14,"score":235,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T09:58:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔死都死左啦,喊黎把撚咩</blockquote><br />\n咁我都祝你快D死老母"},{"pid":"73d08a9a5419611ce41d2f0cc80416ee68346aef","tid":514173,"uid":143454,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T09:58:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b29aa2